#### Companies
#### https://developers.hubspot.com/docs/api/crm/companies

### Basic ###

### List
GET {{baseUrl}}/crm/v3/objects/companies?hapikey={{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Create
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/v3/objects/companies?hapikey={{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "Cambridge",
  "domain": "biglytics.net",
  "industry": "Technology",
  "name": "Biglytics",
  "phone": "(877) 929-0687",
  "state": "Massachusetts"
}

### Read
GET {{baseUrl}}/crm/v3/objects/companies/{companyId}?hapikey={{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Update
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/crm/v3/objects/companies/{companyId}?hapikey={{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

